answers.answer: I think it might depend on why u are high risk...I have type 1 diabetes and with my first I went into preterm labor at 30 weeks...after two medications they stopped it...and then at the end I ended up induced with no signs of going into labor at all. I am 24 wks with second and hoping no complications like last time...maybe look up info on ur high risk situation and see if pre term labor is a "side effect"
